'''Alex "Crashdown" Quartararo''' was an [[officer]] in the [[Colonial Fleet]]. Before the [[Fall of the Twelve Colonies]], he was assigned to the [[Battlestar]] ''[[Triton]]''. He survived the [[Cylon]] attack on the Colonies, and joined up with the [[Civilian fleet|fleet]] that left the system to escape the devastation. Quartararo was assigned as an [[Electronic Countermeasures Officer]] to [[Lieutenant]] [[Sharon Valerii]].

{{Stub}} 

