{{Colonial_Fleet_individual_infobox |imageBG= |image= |name=James Jonasson |hideb=y |homeworld= |birth= |death= |hidep= |species=[[Human]] |gender=Male |height= |hair= |eyes= |skin= |hidef=y |family= |hides= |service no= |occupation=Commanding officer, [[Battlestar]] ''[[Triton]]'' |callsign= |hidec= |era= |affiliation=[[Colonial Fleet]] *Battlestar ''Triton'' }}
'''James Jonasson''' was an officer in the [[Colonial Fleet]]. Several years prior to the [[Cylon]] [[Fall of the Twelve Colonies|assault]] that decimated the [[Twelve Colonies]], Jonasson held the rank of [[Commander]] and was in command of the [[Battlestar]] ''[[Triton]]''. During his tenure in command, he filed disciplinary charges against [[Junior Lieutenant]] [[Kara Thrace]], who was serving as part of the ''Triton''{{'s}} [[air wing]].
==Appearances== *''[[The Son Also Rises]]'' {{Doc}} [[Category:Battlestar commanders]] [[Category:Colonial Fleet officers]] [[Category:Humans]] [[Category:Males]] [[Category:Individuals]]

'''Battlestar Group 39''' was a military formation of the [[Colonial Fleet]] which included the [[Battlestar]] ''[[Triton]]''.<ref name="Ep33">''[[33]]''</ref> The Group was part of the [[Aerilon Combat 5th Division]].<ref name="SAR">''[[The Son Also Rises]]''</ref>

