==Notes and references==
{{Reflist}}
[[Category:Battlestar Groups]]

'''Picon Fleet Headquarters''' was a military installation operated by the [[Colonial Fleet]]. Located in orbit of the [[planet]] [[Picon]], it was responsible for coordinating Colonial Forces throughout the [[Twelve Colonies]]. During the surprise [[Cylon]] [[Fall of the Twelve Colonies|attack]] on the Twelve Colonies forty years after the [[Cylon War]], Picon Fleet Headquarters was destroyed in the first wave of the assault.
