The '''''Solaria''''' was a [[Battlestar]] serving in the [[Colonial Fleet]] following the [[Cylon War]]. When the [[Cylon]]s launched their surprise [[Fall of the Twelve Colonies|attack]] against the [[Twelve Colonies]], the ''Solaria'' survived the initial assault. Following the destruction of [[Picon Fleet Headquarters]], the ''Solaria'' was destroyed by Cylon forces.

